      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic and reliable ride! This car is in good condition, having been well-cared for and maintained throughout its life. While you might find a few minor signs of normal wear and tear, it offers a smooth, dependable driving experience and is ready for many more miles of adventure. It's a wonderful choice for anyone seeking a solid, high-quality vehicle that delivers great value!",
