      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that requires immediate attention. The exterior shows heavy wear with substantial rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed, but it offers a complete set of components for someone looking to rebuild or salvage.",
